name: Precipice
description: I made this audio visual piece to present one of my very first Endlesss.fm rifffs in 2019. I stepped into the space timid, but curious and inspired.. It has been a monumental experience amongst an extraordinary community. Now I find myself stepping into a new space, timid, but curious and inspired. Happy to share the stems with collectors who credit me @littlewingart via twitter. This is my 1st mint on Hicetnunc, hope you enjoy it.
